                        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    
ø
        This is the Licenseware section of Mushroom PD. In this section,
    you can acquire fully-registered versions of any kind of programs,
    ranging from games, to utilitys. The prices in this section are
    specified by the entrant, and cannot be changed in any way. The
    contents of the disks are not PD, and cannot also be exchanged for any
    other disks.
    
        At the moment, the library only has around seven titles, so it is
